{"tid":1009088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期置頂] 台灣推出 教網民向支那舉報翻牆5毛教學","createTime":"2019-02-05T02:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T12:54:00.000Z","uid":54373,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"29755fcef8917c784cd5bc99ec2c3b29434e293b","tid":1009088,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:54:32.000Z","msg":"常常在臉書、YouTube 上看到各種從大陸翻牆過來的網友，發表各種侵略性的言論嗎？現在有方法可以「回敬」他們了，而且是 100% 合法的方式，利用中國的中央網信辦 (國家互聯網信息辦公室)，檢舉違法利用 VPN 等翻牆軟體過來的民眾，將留言截圖 (越多越好)，就可以請這些網民「回家」吃自己啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-0&h=30091da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 點擊上方連結進入中央網信辦，點擊「違法和不良信息舉報入口」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-1&h=88b57acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 接著會有個舉報須知，大概看一下就好 XD 不過看完滑到最下面有個同意需要按一下才能繼續下一步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-2&h=9a00d522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 舉報分類選擇「其它」類。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-3&h=22bcb247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 接著點擊「匿名用戶舉報」，舉報平台選擇「客戶端 APP」，將 APP 名稱打上，並將 APP 官方的網址也貼上，最後舉報內容填寫違反使用 VPN 等類似陳述即可，因為最重要的截圖，有越多截圖越好，點擊「請選擇附件」來上傳，最後輸入驗證碼後按下繼續舉報即可。另外，同樣重要的是，請將繁體字通通都轉成簡體字，繁轉簡傳送門也準備好啦～舉報成功後會收到一組查詢碼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-4&h=bf6b8afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 未來可以在同一個平台上查詢舉報處理進度！是不是覺得很新奇 XD 大家如果遇到翻牆網民來挑釁，就用這招回敬吧！學起來了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n國家互聯網信息辦公室：<a href=\"http://www.12377.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.12377.cn%2F&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFkKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=c438914b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.12377.cn/</a>"},{"pid":"f2071c71c20dfd0cd1b6da5704230275749672d7","tid":1009088,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:55:33.000Z","msg":"以夷制夷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a31652260f3550c273bc657ab1165650547a70c","tid":1009088,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f37580517bd183d4fc0d7a09e897e925a0d8c22","tid":1009088,"uid":41423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:59:38.000Z","msg":"可能係政府許可既呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4709d58309f8ef0a76064bf55ce5afcf5218694","tid":1009088,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:05:29.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n呢啲真係做實事"},{"pid":"18dff181c5169a21f1b059cb334c7c0e57e000e6","tid":1009088,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f37580517bd183d4fc0d7a09e897e925a0d8c22","tid":1009088,"uid":41423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:59:38.000Z","msg":"可能係政府許可既呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:11:16.000Z","msg":"我估會搞到班網軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府5毛就無事"},{"pid":"ec1a74d029b96be83bc906f4f04758d8c32fe4d5","tid":1009088,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d9ea741b6842d99278fddf18be6f8265be05d2","tid":1009088,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ff84851631bd